<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2910105" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">大概相当于知道《神雕侠侣》会由于正来拍那么绝望。<br><br>整个搭配完全是鼻涕绿幽默。<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/a514aa8e530bf72196b702ea7a91d89c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="929" data-rawheight="588" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="929" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/a514aa8e530bf72196b702ea7a91d89c_r.jpg"><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/a8614142450241e427aa04218c6af03f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="349" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/a8614142450241e427aa04218c6af03f_r.jpg">对不起不玩游戏的我关于ls的梗我真的看不懂%&gt;_&lt;%
<a href="/question/26817894/answer/34238245" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
